    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>After making another batch of your ham and bean soup, I had some slices of bacon leftover&#8230;so I decided to try a naughty version of oatmeal influenced by this recipe as well. I used rolled oats and water, but I first toasted my oats in the bacon fat from one slice of bacon. I had the finished oatmeal with toasted walnuts, a teensy bit of brown sugar, and half a slice of crumbled bacon (the other half went missing while I was waiting for the oatmeal to cook). Delicious!</p>
    </div>

