      <p>This oatmeal is awesome! It smells like peanut butter cookies, and tastes even better. Thank you for posting, and I&#39;ll be buying Megan&#39;s book. P.S. I got an advanced copy of Delancey about a month ago, and it&#39;s really charming and warm and honest&#8230;I&#39;ll never forgive Bon Appetit for dropping your column!</p>
    </div>

