  <li id="comment-41383" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/10251368515468569899" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">cjohnson27</a></cite></div>
