    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I never thought I&#39;d be fanatic about oatmeal but this recipe is truly delicious. I&#39;ve already made it twice this week and am already planning to make it again. I have been using a shortcut that works well for me though (especially being 7+ months pregnant with a 32 pound toddler on my hip); after I toast the oats in butter, I add the milk and water to the same pan, bring to a boil and then reduce to a simmer. Yum!</p>
    </div>

