    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Elizabeth</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2014/01/a-good-person-to-know/#comment-41389"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2015-02-26T10:19:33-05:00">Thursday, February 26, 2015 at 10:19 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks for the recipe! I made it before bed last night, and we loved it at breakfast. Here in Switzerland we get oats that aren&#39;t steel cut, but seem to be less processed than North American rolled oats. They&#39;re heftier, and take longer to cook. They worked perfectly in this. We loved the texture and flavour to this oatmeal, and I think it&#39;s going to change my usual morning procedure. </p>
    </div>

