      <p>Susan, I&#8217;m sorry for the confusion!  To the best of my knowledge, the &#8220;subscribe&#8221; thingie beneath the comment window is not a way of subscribing to the blog; it just means that you want to receive notifications whenever someone comments on this particular post. (And you probably don&#8217;t want that, unless you asked a question in the comments and are waiting for a reply!) That said, I&#8217;m not sure why the SUBSCRIBE link in the sidebar isn&#8217;t working for you.  Hmm.  I just tried it myself in both Safari and Chrome, and it worked normally.  Do you have the latest version of Safari?  I wonder if it&#8217;s a software issue&#8230;</p>
